&lt;br&gt;(Nick Bostrom)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + time_of_perils_exit + living_in_simulation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If most observers like us are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 14 time_of_perils_exit → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WG1v20YS%2FisD43qVfLJE6l1yfYBiy21wdhLYDooiDpQVuRK3JrnsLmlaTd3ffrO7pLSyKViA0C%2BJTA6feeZ1Z%2Fb7kU8XJAvTc%2B7To%2FFRqwVnZ2dwJwiLIeXgCfLnCn%2FkMdxnbcftQs5F6D8ymkPuztqz3qw%2Fc7sztw81mfIE3H5dIdzHiDSRMouSlPEYvAABx%2BBAQgT3AkZCheeO2uDCgogZyclqFmQRiWX5og0kZhEJ5UzyiOYBScs3PVhkaSZo8cEsImlKxSxnaTDzmfR4FqcsXpbifYi5%2FXy29fWaRxdSFtEZX8wSKhiqpU9srRLtC9mj%2BpjFM8miLCTKLm3mlHgBkI2tTAKBT6s0wN8LFlJAV25eyxakyhbi%2B7IBgqL%2FWUwlcKHBBD1BF5GIokVM4vM0oMZ7P0o0O%2FY0xil4PEq4VFauBfDb2KeIiI%2BY1GgyJbFPQh5TiDDAYRO%2BreM3ffymqKrP6VNCvRQ%2FfCRhRoEvNMIm1E0N9o7KFObZCjKlRn0oqW3YGCbvQZIFTVdQu6F%2BzrkPNyhEhBfUDcbP0w%2FTm8nd9ALmK1jSmAqS0mayKrOL%2Buhz21nH%2BLKBAUwNJeVPRNJYn2OPilQZHnGBCbX2mzSyxikkSUJGZRNuV1Ez5MuYC0yq2vek14Bk1Huuaywds5HzA5y%2FP9WSc5oS8zQRfE7mLGQpEplzZbyvSuOL0wD3axMuiZdy1EkENVAokKhIxGkDJAeq0oOLJcZv%2BiW%2FmFz91vrXV5jTkOeY%2BupbHWf6hL%2FDFX6O2OhbjYW6%2FcxLTUQwhhQTFs03CXxRpDScYRGBksaHJyqJ4T%2FgkZTIVPAEP1PlEWc6YUHlJBEnBqGId%2B2GRJKuWrfouxj%2Bdn5orQQ8SvjAhR%2BQTMLfbrOnHp6iojMMBpTVhM4zxTLFWrnGNsKUswUKvfL2GNra4WPoOM91zVd6JKQnWVKat07Dgh0zjwPyJxE%2B5OhYdJkXcuUuskCyEBmVJMZoiRVImqYhjdDzUPsofPS49gbCG5an4FOPC0GxelHNRhzdH%2BPfWE5IyHYdxuYBjdxU%2FDlXPSRDBmfrPKm5DRgZkz7VNqI