. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 15 space_expansion_backfires" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1v2zgS%2FiuD4PbOzvlF8rudywFp4%2BwWm3SLJEWxqAuXlmiLF0nUkVQUbzf723dISracyIgBf2kVefjMM6%2Bc0Y8Tny5JGqr33Kcnk5N2G87Pz%2BFeEBaD4uAJ8scaH7IYZmnHcXuQcRH6j4xmkLnzzrw%2FH8zdPtSk4gm4%2Fbo%2BPosR5kLKNEoU4zF4AaJNwIGECO4FjIQazB13wIUlEXOSkfU8SCMSy%2BKHDpCYRSSUc8kjmgVEFb%2F0YZmqVND8wDwiSlExz5gK5j6THk9jxeJVIT6AmJffz3dOb3j0QSbEo3P6lOBrJD1fEO9hyQSVxpop8QIgW5OYBAKf1irA5yULKaC7tj%2FLNihNmfi%2BbICg6GMWUwlcGDBBm%2BgJElEkziS%2BVwG1TvqXROtiz2CcgcejhEttzEYAz8Y%2BRUR8xSw1qUjsk5DHFCIMYtiC75sYTR%2B%2Fa6r6OFpGPYUHH0mYUuBLg7ANZ8uAvaNSwSJdQ6rV6IOSlg2bwMUHkGRJ1Rpqt9TPOPfhFoWI8IK6xfh5%2BnF6e3E%2FvYTFGlY0poIo2krWRQZRn6kdZ53ijw2Mk7KUtD8RyWB9jj0qlDY84gLzZuM3aWWtU0iShIzKFtyto1bIVzEXmDu1H0m%2FAcm4%2F1w3WCZmY%2BcneP%2FhzEguqCL2bSL4gixYyBQSWXBtvK%2FT%2F6vTAPdbC66IpzjqJIJaKBRIdCRi1QDJger04GKF8Zt%2BzS4vrn9v%2F%2BMbLGjIM8xwfdbEmT7hc7jG44iNvjVYqNtPPWUjgjGkmIBovs3Tyzxz4RxrBbQ0vmwqFlH4N3hEEakET%2FCYroI4JSY5dU4S0bQIebxrtySSdN2%2BQ9%2FF8JfzU3st4FHCRy78gKQS%2FnJbff3yDBWdYzCgKBp0nqmNd3lB3GC3YNrfAuVeORzLvOV0jNv14%2BC5bmgrwSLNaycTc4JZoAsIMwg9s6k%2FXSRERDZ3A%2FIHET7ULmnqx3SNXvZTEjZTk5toEGd%2Bm4sFU5ghLF4K7RV0KYKfwReKpSdkhP1BagaBCYlAdy9RBx6QNFw2ZbpcMo%2FR2MPoyHqefZdoLkaGLpf6PzxcinOCFhGxxiDHVB%2FF5wa8m179dju1uWoQMspWge47DWSKiRZhN4tVE5uWF6AHNq6Du883Nxe3v9sswNZhlWB1PlDfIC24oh7UdHrAxcdLDKtgBKvDJlW9BffoqGUahnnCNRfrpn0CrGT2aFPDlqClhh6xBlkxYxN%2FpLFBxZ6CiZ0KfMzLNmSPmMLMxjBkcUFM%2Fj9lq1VI24ahbP%2BH%2Bf9tFS9tSzI1gkWPtaaLHw1HmN8%2BTiEJidWV90Xi655BHyk6dtOZsIMS1Km7EdrOYtRtELCGrKRte5imPE1%2BZdqz8SUJ15%2Bo%2BCz96iQdtAad8bg76o9Hbqc7dFzadPqbrHUcdzgeDbs91xkO%2B25n6PbyPH4RP%2BxhJgny2tUE5g%2BWwU7A%2FvkyXGc2VNvITF75sQy28ecsXvlv2ab5O72SMZ2DyK%2F8oymv%2FBJREi0PYdotub3jHsQUkY%2Bmihhlriw6hKtboto%2FjCq2vaOpsqhEVQXhW1TdVtGAe8ODWCLm0SwRo8RSZsmbLDuOk9Mc9jBjD6uwLDm%2BsLKkxDRjob9IV%2FJNuoMN3VHnULoF%2BNGcC6Cyiz1BM2ySb2Zu