morganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_5_7.drawio" id="w1_2_5_7"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#eec2a8;strokeColor=#c65a2e;fontColor=#5a2a10;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="433" y="542" width="395" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Suffering-focused&lt;br&gt;ethics&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+8]&lt;br&gt;→ The Humane League&lt;br&gt;   73 lives-eq/$1k · 100% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up GiveWell top charity (AMF) · 0%&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 8 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWH9z2zYS%2FSo7nutVyskUSf2W65tRYrnN1EkztnOdTpRRIBKScKYIHgCaVlP3s98CICXKkmum%2BsdDU8Dbt4u3i11%2BPQnpnKSResNDejI8aTbh%2FPwcbgVhMSgOgSC%2Fr%2FEhi2GS%2Bq7XhoyLKLxnNIPMm%2FrTzrQPNal4Av263jqJEWIkZbpKFOMxBEtEGoILCRE8WDISaSBv4IMHcyKmJCPr6TJdkVgWP%2FhAYrYikZxKvqLZkqjilw7MU5UKmm%2BYrohSVEwzppbTkMmAp7Fi8aJY3geZzudU4KvpnAeppKGhNybBEsiWI5NA4MNaLfF5ziIK6Pv2Z9kEpTmQMJQNEBQDxmIqgQsDJugpukZWFJkwie%2FVklqvv5dINw4MxhkEfJVwqdltFuDeOKSIiK%2BYNGhSkTgkEY8prPBEIge%2BbAI%2Bvv%2Biqert9CGhgcKN9yRKKfC5QdiejWPAXlOpYJauIdVm9EZJy44N4RaxftKxpHBFySKlduOP4%2Ffj69Ht%2BAJma1jQmAqiqJOsCw3QkKmdCL3CHxsQc2V56CAiksH6GAdUKO3tigs8%2FU2wpF1rI0GSJGJUOnCzXjkRX8RcoAJqX5NOA5JB57FusMxBDdzv4M3bM7NyRhWxbxPBZ2TGIqaQyIxrj0Mt4E9uA7zPDlySQHG0SQS1ULgg0eGPVQMkB6o1wcUCD238KbsYXf3W%2FMdnmNGIZ6hTvdccLn3A52iN2x